HEADWORD: Sarcobasis
<hw>Sar*cob"a*sis</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Sarcobases</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[NL.,
